steps.html_instructions: Head east on Cadillac Square toward Bates St
Take the 2nd right onto Randolph Street

Turn right onto M-10 N/Jefferson Ave
Continue to follow M-10 N
Take exit 2A for I-75 toward Toledo/Flint
Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-75 S/Toledo

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-75 S/Toledo and merge onto I-75 S
Entering Ohio
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-75 S

Keep left at the fork to stay on I-75 S
Entering Kentucky
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-71 S, follow signs for Louisville
Take exit 5 on the left for I-264/Watterson Expy
Exit 5 turns slightly left and becomes I-264 W
Take exit 12 for I-65 N/KY-61/I-65 S toward Indianapolis/Nashville
Keep left, follow signs for I-65 S/Nashville/I-65 N/Downtown/Louisville/Indianapolis

Keep left at the fork, follow signs for I-65 S/Nashville and merge onto I-65 S
Entering Tennessee
Keep right at the fork to stay on I-65 S, follow signs for I-40 W/Huntsville/Memphis

Keep right at the fork to stay on I-65 S, follow signs for Huntsville
Entering Alabama
Take exit 171 for Interstate 85 N/Day Street toward Atlanta
Keep left, follow signs for Interstate 85 N/Atlanta
Continue onto I-85 N
Take exit 1 for Court St
Continue onto Arba St (signs for Alabama State Univ)
Turn right onto S Decatur St

Sharp left onto S Union St
Destination will be on the right
